    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、貴方まだいたの？　相変わらず仕事の虫ね\n少しは休まないと体に悪いわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you're still here? You're as much of a workaholic as ever. You really should take a break.\nWorking without a break is bad for your health.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、莉央さんが忘れ物を取りに事務所に来るって\n葵から聞いたので、待っていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I heard from Aoi that you were coming to the office to pick up something‚ Rio-san.\nSo‚ I was waiting for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "待っていた？　もしかして次のライブのこと？\n何か問題でもあったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waiting for me? Is it about the next live?\nIs there some sort of problem?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、琴乃から聞いてます。莉央さんが\n『星の海の記憶』を歌うことに躊躇してるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Kotono. She mentioned that you were hesitating about\nsinging \"Memories of the Starry Sky\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その話\nそれなら、さっき琴乃にも言ったけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that topic.\nWell‚ I told Kotono earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい！\n結論を出す前に俺の話を聞いてくれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait!\nBefore you make a decision‚ would you listen to what I have to say?",
        "id": ""
